## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="12fa8-103">이 예제에서는 <xref:System.Activities.Variable%601>을 사용하여 메시지 문자열을 포함합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="12fa8-103">In this example, a <xref:System.Activities.Variable%601> is used to hold a message string.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="12fa8-104">이 메시지는 <xref:System.Activities.Statements.WriteLine> 작업에 의해 콘솔 창에 작성됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="12fa8-104">This message is written to the console window by a <xref:System.Activities.Statements.WriteLine> activity.</span></span>  

```csharp  
Variable<string> msg =   
    new Variable<string>() { Default = "Hello World!" };  

Activity wf = new Sequence()  
{  
    Variables =   
    {  
        msg  
    },  
    Activities =  
    {  
        new WriteLine()  
        {  
            Text = msg  
        }  
    }  
};  
```
